<tag name="PERSON" value="start"/>Ljubek<tag name="PERSON" value="end"/> later became vice-president of the <tag name="ORGANIZATION" value="start"/>Croatian Olympic Committee<tag name="ORGANIZATION" value="end"/> and served as chef de mission for the <tag name="ORGANIZATION" value="start"/>Croatian Olympic team<tag name="ORGANIZATION" value="end"/>.
